{"type": "article", "id": 20242, "title": "六边形羊毛挂件", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-05T07:00:17Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606144411s5MoVd7NWOiDq2XY.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tFilzFelt 是美国波士顿的一家用羊毛织物做设计的品牌，由两位女设计师创立。这是一组近似六边形的羊毛挂件，有 5 种不同的模型，上面有不同稀疏程度的树叶状的镂空，可以相互拼接组成屏风。挂件可以订制，根据颜色或者镂空图案组合成渐变的图像，让办公空间或居家空间有了生气。售价 3 美元起，<a href=\"http://filzfelt.com/index.php?/shop/product/link\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061444088J6RrBIUTCNSyfDd.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144408lCLPHkYgr0aMW5tZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144409iUmo0kzIqEeZhxp1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061444091xPaJ2YhQXdRv0ew.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.49666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606144410KakX4xEW81AljUcY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061444100ug5yWQJ9wclbZod.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}